---
import contribution1 from "../assets/contribution_1.png";
import portfolio from "../assets/portfolio.png";
---

<div id="projects" class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900 py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
      Contributions
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-4">
      Here are some contributions I have made.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img src={contribution1.src} alt="Open Source Contribution" class="w-full h-48 object-cover" />
            <div class="p-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white">
                Open Source Contribution - Flutter Plugin
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2 text-justify">
                I contributed to the open-source Flutter plugin 
                <strong>app_settings</strong>, improving compatibility by adding 
                support for Swift Package Manager (SPM). This enhancement 
                facilitates easier dependency management for iOS developers. 
                The contribution involved analyzing the pluginâ€™s architecture, 
                integrating SPM support, and ensuring smooth functionality 
